&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apesar da simplicidade dos slides e do escopo reduzido, ainda assim faz√™-los me tomou mais de 10 horas de trabalho. √â um processo constante de lapida√ß√£o e melhoria at√© chegar no resultado final. Uso o Google Slides, acho excelente.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;A palestra&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://aurelio.net/curso/sc-dev-summit/aurelio.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Felizmente, o evento foi aqui na minha cidade, Joinville. N√£o precisei me estressar com aeroportos, voos, hot√©is e toda a burocracia normalmente envolvida. Que al√≠vio.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Eu e a Mog almo√ßamos e fomos pro evento, simples assim :)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;O evento foi na Univille, universidade particular que tem uma estrutura excelente. Sal√£o grande, equipamento de som de alta qualidade, dois tel√µes, show de bola.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Tinha cerca de 150 pessoas durante minha palestra.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://aurelio.net/curso/sc-dev-summit/publico.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;O in√≠cio, pra mim, √© sempre a pior parte. Fora aquele nervosismozinho besta que sempre d√° nos primeiros momentos, eu j√° quero ir logo pro assunto, que √© o que interessa. Assim, a parte de me apresentar, falar um pouco sobre o que fa√ßo, sempre sai ruim e esquisita.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A Mog vive me falando que eu devia praticar antes, pensar sobre o que vou dizer na hora de me apresentar. Que eu devia falar um pouco do site, dos livros, do meu trabalho, da minha hist√≥ria. Fazer alguma piadinha pra quebrar o gelo. Eu concordo com ela. Eu tento. Mas na hora n√£o sai. N√£o fico confort√°vel falando de mim, parece autopromo√ß√£o, sei l√°. Bobeira minha.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fora a apresenta√ß√£o estranha, dali pra frente tudo fluiu bem. Consegui trazer bastante informa√ß√µes e dicas enquanto passava os slides. O pessoal estava prestando aten√ß√£o, ent√£o fiquei tranquilo. S√≥ n√£o teve muita piadinha, acho que estou perdendo a veia humor√≠stica (ou s√≥ ficando v√©io chato mesmo).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Eu nunca fa√ßo scripts ou ensaios para as palestras, √© sempre de improviso. Tenho uma ideia geral, uma lista de t√≥picos que quero abordar e √© isso. Os slides servem de guia e falo o que vem na cabe√ßa.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;A demonstra√ß√£o ao vivo&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://aurelio.net/curso/sc-dev-summit/demo.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Terminados os slides, era a hora de demonstrar ali ao vivo como √© usar a linha de comando para resolver problemas, exatamente como fa√ßo nos v√≠deos do &lt;a href=&quot;http://aurelio.net/tela-preta/&quot;&gt;Tela Preta&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Abri um terminal em tela cheia, aumentei bem a fonte, coloquei um prompt (&lt;code&gt;$PS1&lt;/code&gt;) bem amig√°vel e comecei a digitar comandos e fazer a locu√ß√£o esportiva, descrevendo o que eu estava fazendo :)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://aurelio.net/curso/sc-dev-summit/historico.txt&quot;&gt;Aqui est√° o hist√≥rico completo dos comandos executados&lt;/a&gt;. Vou destacar a seguir algumas partes dele.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ajustando prompt:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$PS1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;gp&quot;&gt;PS1=&#39;$ &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;
PS1=&#39;&lt;/span&gt;--------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;span class=&quot;se&quot;&gt;\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mostrando como combinar comandos para ir filtrando um texto:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;cat hino.txt
cat hino.txt | head -n 3
cat hino.txt | head -n 3 | tail -n 1
cat hino.txt | head -n 3 | tail -n 1 | cut -d , -f 1
cat hino.txt | head -n 3 | tail -n 1 | cut -d , -f 1 | tr a-z A-z
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Trocar a extens√£o de todos os arquivo de &lt;code&gt;.css&lt;/code&gt; para &lt;code&gt;.sass&lt;/code&gt; (&lt;a href=&quot;http://aurelio.net/blog/2015/06/06/tela-preta-8/&quot;&gt;veja um v√≠deo similar&lt;/a&gt;):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;find . -name &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;*.css&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
find . -name &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;*.css&quot;&lt;/span&gt; | sed &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;s/.*/&amp;amp; &amp;amp;/&#39;&lt;/span&gt;
find . -name &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;*.css&quot;&lt;/span&gt; | sed &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;s/.*/mv &amp;amp; &amp;amp;/&#39;&lt;/span&gt;
find . -name &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;*.css&quot;&lt;/span&gt; | sed &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;s/.*/mv &amp;amp; &amp;amp;/&#39;&lt;/span&gt; | sed &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;s/css$/sass/&#39;&lt;/span&gt;
find . -name &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;*.css&quot;&lt;/span&gt; | sed &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;s/.*/git mv &amp;amp; &amp;amp;/&#39;&lt;/span&gt; | sed &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;s/css$/sass/&#39;&lt;/span&gt;
find . -name &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;*.css&quot;&lt;/span&gt; | sed &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;s/.*/git mv &amp;amp; &amp;amp;/&#39;&lt;/span&gt; | sed &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;s/css$/sass/&#39;&lt;/span&gt; | sh
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contar o n√∫mero de vezes que cada palavra aparece em um texto:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;cat LICENSE | egrep &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;\w+&#39;&lt;/span&gt;
cat LICENSE | egrep -o &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;\w+&#39;&lt;/span&gt;
cat LICENSE | egrep -o &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;\w+&#39;&lt;/span&gt; | tr A-Z a-z
cat LICENSE | egrep -o &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;\w+&#39;&lt;/span&gt; | tr A-Z a-z | sort
cat LICENSE | egrep -o &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;\w+&#39;&lt;/span&gt; | tr A-Z a-z | sort | uniq -c
cat LICENSE | egrep -o &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;\w+&#39;&lt;/span&gt; | tr A-Z a-z | sort | uniq -c | sort
cat LICENSE | egrep -o &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;\w+&#39;&lt;/span&gt; | tr A-Z a-z | sort | uniq -c | sort -n
cat LICENSE | egrep -o &lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&#39;\w+&#39;&lt;/span&gt; | tr A-Z a-z | sort | uniq -c | sort -n -r
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Usar aliases para criar comandos, e utiliz√°-los:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;alias &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;numeros&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;egrep -o &#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;se&quot;&gt;\d&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;+&#39;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;alias &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;conta&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&quot;egrep -o &#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;se&quot;&gt;\w&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;+&#39; | tr A-Z a-z | sort | uniq -c | sort -n -r | head -n 5&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
cat LICENSE | conta
cat LICENSE | conta | numeros
cat LICENSE | conta | numeros | pbcopy
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pra quem usa Mac, o &lt;code&gt;pbcopy&lt;/code&gt; copia a sa√≠da do comando anterior para a √Årea de Transfer√™ncia. A√≠ √© s√≥ colar (&lt;code&gt;Command-V&lt;/code&gt;) em outra janela, ou usar o &lt;code&gt;pbpaste&lt;/code&gt; em outro terminal.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;O sorteio dos livros, usando shell&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;No final da palestra, sorteei dois livros meus, o &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.shellscript.com.br&quot;&gt;Shell Script Profissional&lt;/a&gt; que eu levei um exemplar que eu tinha aqui em casa, e o &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.piazinho.com.br&quot;&gt;Express√µes Regulares&lt;/a&gt;, que a Novatec Editora enviou de cortesia para os organizadores do evento.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Reaproveitei uma ideia que tive l√° em 2004, numa &lt;a href=&quot;http://aurelio.net/curso/linuxchix/&quot;&gt;palestra de 3h&lt;/a&gt; üò± que dei no II Encontro Nacional LinuxChix-BR: usar a shell para gerar um n√∫mero aleat√≥rio e ganha o sorteio quem tiver aquele n√∫mero &lt;strong&gt;impresso&lt;/strong&gt; em algum documento, cart√£o, papel, o que for. Foi bem divertido!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;$((&lt;/span&gt;RANDOM &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;%&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;99999&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;))&lt;/span&gt;   &lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# 5 d√≠gitos&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;$((&lt;/span&gt;RANDOM &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;%&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;9999&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;))&lt;/span&gt;    &lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# 4 d√≠gitos&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;$((&lt;/span&gt;RANDOM &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;%&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;999&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;))&lt;/span&gt;     &lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# 3 d√≠gitos&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Essa √© uma foto &lt;a href=&quot;http://aurelio.net/curso/linuxchix/&quot;&gt;l√° de 2004&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://aurelio.net/curso/linuxchix/papeis.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

